#: ../../tutorial/get-event-waveform.md:1
msgid "Get Event Waveform"
msgstr "获取事件波形"

#: ../../tutorial/get-event-waveform.md:3
msgid ""
"Since v0.6.0, HinetPy supports requesting event waveform data via {meth}"
"`~HinetPy.client.Client.get_event_waveform`."
msgstr ""
"从v0.6.0开始，HinetPy可以通过 {meth}"
"`~HinetPy.client.Client.get_event_waveform` 申请事件波形数据。"

#: ../../tutorial/get-event-waveform.md:6
msgid ""
"Following is a simple example code to request waveforms of events in a "
"specified time range, magnitude and depth."
msgstr "下面是一个申请时间范围、震级、深度内的事件的波形的示例。"

#: ../../tutorial/get-event-waveform.md:22
msgid "You can also limit events to a specified region by three ways:"
msgstr "你可以用三种方式进一步限制事件的区域范围:"

#: ../../tutorial/get-event-waveform.md:24
msgid "specify region code"
msgstr "指定区域代码"

#: ../../tutorial/get-event-waveform.md:25
msgid "specify a box region"
msgstr "指定矩形区域"

#: ../../tutorial/get-event-waveform.md:26
msgid "specify a circular region"
msgstr "指定环形区域"

#: ../../tutorial/get-event-waveform.md:28
msgid ""
"See {meth}`~HinetPy.client.Client.get_event_waveform` for more available "
"options."
msgstr "更多可用选项见 {meth}`~HinetPy.client.Client.get_event_waveform`。"
